  <h1>What is BMI? Body Mass Index Fully Explained</h1>
  <div class="meta">Last updated: May 2025 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 6 min read &nbsp;·&nbsp; Reviewed for accuracy</div>

  <p>BMI, or Body Mass Index, is one of the most widely used tools in the world for assessing whether a person has a healthy body weight relative to their height. Doctors, health organisations, and researchers use it daily — yet many people are unsure exactly what it measures and what its limitations are.</p>

